Version:        24.12.1
Release:        0
Summary:        Base package of kdepim
License:        GPL-2.0-only AND GPL-2.0-or-later AND LGPL-2.1-or-later
URL:            https://www.kde.org
Source0:        https://download.kde.org/stable/release-service/%{version}/src/%{name}-%{version}.tar.xz
%if %{with released}
